title: Napalm 101
author: Falkenzz
pages:
#- Need:
Gasoline
Styrofoam
Container
#- Mix styrofoam with gasoline. You will need a lot of styrofoam. Keep pushing styrofoam into your container until you run out or the mixture is an even paste. 
#- Use:
This mixture is extremely flamable. Once it is lit, it will take a lot to put it out. It will stick to almost anything. The choice is yours on how to get it to the target and how to light it.
#- NOTICE: EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY
#- 